headline: L3Harris Wins Contract to Produce Propulsion for Javelin Weapon System
summary: LHX secures a record $292 million deal to produce Javelin propulsion systems, boosting production for the next five years.

headline: Northrop Grumman: Strong Backlog And FCF Generation Justify Higher Valuation
summary: Northrop Grumman (NOC) remains a Buy with a raised price target of $634, reflecting strong fundamentals and a 10% upside potential.
